{"tha-ap375:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap375:0.2":"Bodhivandanavagga ","tha-ap375:0.3":"3 Tinuppalamaliyattheraapadana ","tha-ap375:1.1":"“Candabhaganaditire, ","tha-ap375:1.2":"ahosim vanaro tada; ","tha-ap375:1.3":"Addasam virajam buddham, ","tha-ap375:1.4":"nisinnam pabbatantare. ","tha-ap375:2.1":"Obhasentam disa sabba, ","tha-ap375:2.2":"salarajamva phullitam; ","tha-ap375:2.3":"Lakkhanabyanjanupetam, ","tha-ap375:2.4":"disvanattamano aham. ","tha-ap375:3.1":"Udaggacitto sumano, ","tha-ap375:3.2":"pitiya hatthamanaso; ","tha-ap375:3.3":"Tini uppalapupphani, ","tha-ap375:3.4":"matthake abhiropayim. ","tha-ap375:4.1":"Pujayitvana pupphani, ","tha-ap375:4.2":"phussassaham mahesino; ","tha-ap375:4.3":"Sagaravo bhavitvana, ","tha-ap375:4.4":"pakkamim uttaramukho. ","tha-ap375:5.1":"Gacchanto patikutiko, ","tha-ap375:5.2":"vippasannena cetasa; ","tha-ap375:5.3":"Selantare patitvana, ","tha-ap375:5.4":"papunim jivitakkhayam. ","tha-ap375:6.1":"Tena kammena sukatena, ","tha-ap375:6.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","tha-ap375:6.3":"Jahitva purimam jatim, ","tha-ap375:6.4":"tavatimsamagacchaham. ","tha-ap375:7.1":"Satanam tinikkhattunca, ","tha-ap375:7.2":"devarajjamakarayim; ","tha-ap375:7.3":"Satanam pancakkhattunca, ","tha-ap375:7.4":"cakkavatti ahosaham. ","tha-ap375:8.1":"Dvenavute ito kappe, ","tha-ap375:8.2":"yam pupphamabhipujayim; ","tha-ap375:8.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap375:8.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap375:9.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap375:9.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap375:9.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap375:10.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma tinuppalamaliyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap375:11.1":"Tinuppalamaliyattherassapadanam tatiyam. "}